            <pb n="1v"/>
            <p>Darf ich Sie bitten, theurer <lb/>
                    <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118529250">Ehrenberg</persName>, den
               Ueberbringer <lb/>dieser Zeilen Herrn Bernhard <lb/>
                    <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118522396">Cotta</persName>, einen talentvollen <lb/>Geognosten aus <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/2822939">Tharand</placeName>
               <lb/>bei <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/2935022">Dresden</placeName>, <ref xml:id="a9f5849a-fb02-462c-b584-9afb02f62cac" corresp="#c9101849-a569-46cd-9018-49a56926cd4e">der so schön <lb/>die versteinten Hölzer <lb/>untersucht hat</ref>
                    <note xml:id="c9101849-a569-46cd-9018-49a56926cd4e" corresp="#a9f5849a-fb02-462c-b584-9afb02f62cac">
                     <bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/v8/UBERKVN5">Cotta 1832</bibl>
                  </note>, freundlichst <lb/>aufzunehmen. </p>
            <closer rend="paragraph">
               <signed>AlHumboldt</signed>
               <dateline rend="align(left)">Donnerstags</dateline>
            </closer>
